Package org.cloudbus.cloudsim.plus.util

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CustomLog
    Replaces the primitive functionality of the standard CloudSim Log.
    ExperimentDefinition
    A definition/description of an experiment.
    ExperimentsRunner
    A utility that runs a set of experiments in different JVM processes.
    Id
    A factory for CloudSim entities' ids.
    InMemoryBufferredHandler
    Keeps in memory a buffer of log records with a predefined size.
    TextUtil
    This is a utility class for transforming beans and other classes into consistent and well aligned text.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    Textualize
    Type annotation, which specifies which properties of a class should be used for printing/textualizing.
